---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Em Breve">
	<main class="text-center space-y-8 animate-in fade-in duration-1000">
		<div class="relative inline-block">
			<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
				SURF BITS
			</h1>
			<div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 md:-top-8 md:-right-8 bg-brand-primary text-white text-xs md:text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full rotate-12 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
				EM BREVE
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
			A melhor curadoria de equipamentos e ofertas de surf está chegando. 
			Prepare-se para surfar com o melhor setup.
		</p>
		
		<div class="h-1 w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 mx-auto rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
		
		<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase">
			2025 • surf-bits.com
		</p>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
